a><br />\n<br />\n中西區區議會在財務委員會上，通過停止邀請中聯辦代作為區議會撥款活動嘉賓。民主派質疑中聯辦派員出席地區活動，有滲透社區宣傳之嫌，亦不應讓團體以區議會撥款申辨活動作政治表忠。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務專員黃何詠詩多次反駁議員，認為不能限制活動邀請嘉賓，需要與民政總署再作討論，又指「睇唔到請中聯辦有幾干預香港自治」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁想請佢，叫佢辭職咪唔係中聯辦囉，到時點邀都得"},{"pid":"87d28c50b284a2f0fd325e4fcbd5dbc2d3accf7a","tid":1921883,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4180a5c484293f58190b8da7e5f023f892289ee5","tid":1921883,"uid":319216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">民主黨吳兆康要求楊哲安收回中聯辦人員等同外國領事的言論，指責他企圖破壞一國兩制，將中國稱為外國，「我勸你收返個言論。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87040c1e6ecc38826d1a65064b0461c635081f63","tid":1921883,"uid":229479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:09:14.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"3f856dade5f120018cf941244dd8f060d560f637","tid":1921883,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bfbe13596191e9e514dee42105ef648a9c0e2a","tid":1921883,"uid":185854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6d200c8e5c9b570e4e8af9862c5c5e05652ae20","tid":1921883,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T09:55:44.000Z","msg":"其他區都學下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺中西區好似好多第一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:13:12.000Z","msg":"中西區始終知識水平較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n素人好多都係三大出身<br />\n<br />\n中西區班白鴿又唔係傳統白鴿，你睇許智勇就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/n